dct_title_s: Map Showing the New Exterior Line for Solid Filling & for Piers on the South Side of the Manasquan River
dct_description_sm: Map covers Manasquan River along the New York and Long Branch Railroad Bridge. Map shows exterior line for solid filling and pier line, as well as the public Road Bridge. Included with map is a paper copy.
